      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-CJIIL03-CALL-RTN.

           INITIALIZE     XCJIIL03-IN

      *    그룹회사코드
           MOVE  BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  XCJIIL03-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *    구분코드
           MOVE  '4'
             TO  XCJIIL03-I-DSTCD
      *    년월일
           MOVE  JICOM-BF-BZOPR-YMD
            TO   XCJIIL03-I-YMD
      *    일수/월수
           MOVE  1
             TO  XCJIIL03-I-NODAY-NOMN

      *@1 공통 UTILITY CALL
           #DYCALL     CJIIL03  YCCOMMON-CA  XCJIIL03-CA

      *@1 RETURN 정보 확인
           IF  XCJIIL03-R-STAT    =  ZEROS

               MOVE  XCJIIL03-O-YMD
                 TO  WK-BASEYMD
           ELSE
               #ERROR XCJIIL03-R-ERRCD
                      XCJIIL03-R-TREAT-CD
                      XCJIIL03-R-STAT
           END-IF
           .

       S3100-CJIIL03-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
