      *@  대주주(특수관계인 포함)에
      *        대한 신용공여 현황조회 (헤더)
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3200-QJL4136-CALL-RTN.

      *@2.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL4136-IN

      *@2.2 호출변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL4136-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월
           MOVE XDJL4136-I-BASE-YMD(1:6)
             TO XQJL4136-I-BASE-YM

      *    기준일
           MOVE XDJL4136-I-BASE-YMD(7:2)
             TO XQJL4136-I-BASE-DD

240926*    기준년월일
           MOVE XDJL4136-I-BASE-YMD
             TO XQJL4136-I-BASE-YMD

      *@2.3 프로그램 호출
           #DYSQLA QJL4136 XQJL4136-CA
      *@2.4 호출결과확인
           IF COND-DBSQL-OK OR COND-DBSQL-MRNF
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
              #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF

      *@   업무규제자기자본
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-BZWK-REGUL-ONCP
                 = XQJL4136-O-BZWK-REGUL-ONCP / 1000000

      *@   자기자본기준년월
           MOVE XDJL4136-I-BASE-YMD(1:6)
             TO XDJL4136-O-ONCP-BASE-YM

      *    대주주 신용공여한도
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-STKLN-M-GRCR-LIMT
                 = XQJL4136-O-BZWK-REGUL-ONCP / 1000000 * 0.25


      *    대주주 신용공여잔액
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-STKLN-MAIN-GRCR-BAL
                 = XQJL4136-O-STKLN-MAIN-GRCR-BAL / 1000000

      *    대주주 한도여유액
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-STKLN-ML-SEXTR-AMT
                 = XDJL4136-O-STKLN-M-GRCR-LIMT
                   - XDJL4136-O-STKLN-MAIN-GRCR-BAL

      *    자회사 신용공여한도
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-SBCO-GRCR-LIMT
                 = XQJL4136-O-BZWK-REGUL-ONCP / 1000000 * 0.2

      *    자회사 신용공여잔액
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-SBCO-GRCR-BAL
                 = XQJL4136-O-SBCO-GRCR-BAL / 1000000

      *    자회사 한도여유액
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-SBCO-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT
                 = XDJL4136-O-SBCO-GRCR-LIMT
                   - XDJL4136-O-SBCO-GRCR-BAL

      *    전체 신용공여한도
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-GRCR-LIMT
                 = XQJL4136-O-BZWK-REGUL-ONCP / 1000000 * 0.2

      *    전체 신용공여잔액
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-GRCR-BAL
                 = XDJL4136-O-SBCO-GRCR-BAL
                 + XDJL4136-O-STKLN-MAIN-GRCR-BAL

      *    전체 한도여유액
           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT
                 = XDJL4136-O-GRCR-LIMT
                   - XDJL4136-O-GRCR-BAL

           .
       S3200-QJL4136-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 대주주(특수관계인 포함)에
      *        대한 신용공여 현황조회 (그리드)
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3300-QJL4137-CALL-RTN.

      *@3.1 변수초기화
           INITIALIZE XQJL4137-IN

      *@3.2 변수 MOVE
      *@   그룹회사코드
           MOVE BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO XQJL4137-I-GROUP-CO-CD

      *@   기준년월
           MOVE XDJL4136-I-BASE-YMD(1:6)
             TO XQJL4137-I-BASE-YM

      *    기준일
           MOVE XDJL4136-I-BASE-YMD(7:2)
             TO XQJL4137-I-BASE-DD

240926*    기준년월일
           MOVE XDJL4136-I-BASE-YMD
             TO XQJL4137-I-BASE-YMD

      *    소관부점코드
           IF XDJL4136-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD = '9999'
               MOVE '%%%%'
                 TO XQJL4137-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD

               MOVE '1'
                 TO XQJL4137-I-BRN-DSTIC
240926     ELSE
               MOVE XDJL4136-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD
                 TO WK-JRSDZ-BRNCD

               PERFORM S6000-FJL0001-CALL-RTN
                  THRU S6000-FJL0001-CALL-EXT

               IF XFJL0001-O-BRNCD-VALDN-YN = CO-CHA-1
                   MOVE '2'
                     TO XQJL4137-I-BRN-DSTIC

                   MOVE WK-H-I-BRNCD1
                     TO XQJL4137-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD1

                   MOVE WK-H-I-BRNCD2
                     TO XQJL4137-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD2

                   MOVE SPACE
                     TO XQJL4137-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD

               ELSE
                   MOVE '1'
                     TO XQJL4137-I-BRN-DSTIC

                   MOVE WK-H-I-BRNCD1
                     TO XQJL4137-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD

                   MOVE SPACE
                     TO XQJL4137-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD1

                   MOVE SPACE
                     TO XQJL4137-I-JRSDZ-BRNCD2

               END-IF

           END-IF

      *@3.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL4137 XQJL4137-CA

      *@3.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@3.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   출력건수
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
             TO XDJL4136-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4136-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

               IF XQJL4137-O-JRSD-BRNZ-NAME(WK-I) = '소계' OR '합계'
      *            고객식별자
                   MOVE  SPACE
                     TO  XDJL4136-O-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)
               ELSE
      *            고객식별자
                   MOVE  XQJL4137-O-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)
                     TO  XDJL4136-O-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)
               END-IF

      *        고객명
               MOVE  XQJL4137-O-CUSTNM(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4136-O-CUSTNM(WK-I)

      *        소관부점명
               MOVE  XQJL4137-O-JRSD-BRNZ-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4136-O-JRSD-BRNZ-NAME(WK-I)

      *        신용공여중분류코드
               MOVE  XQJL4137-O-GRCR-MIDL-CLSFI-CD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4136-O-GRCR-MIDL-CLSFI-CD(WK-I)

      *        통화코드1
               MOVE  XQJL4137-O-CNCYCD1(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4136-O-CNCYCD1(WK-I)

      *        이사회승인금액
               MOVE  XQJL4137-O-BRDC-ATHOR-AMT(WK-I)
                 TO  WK-BRDC-ATHOR-AMT

      *         원화가 아닐 경우
               IF XDJL4136-O-CNCYCD1(WK-I) NOT= 'KRW'
                   IF XDJL4136-O-CNCYCD1(WK-I) NOT= SPACE

      *                환율 조회
                       PERFORM  S4000-CJIEX01-CALL-RTN
                          THRU  S4000-CJIEX01-CALL-EXT

      *                달러만 천단위 절사
                       IF XDJL4136-O-CNCYCD1(WK-I) = 'USD'

      *                    이사회승인금액
                           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-BRDC-ATHOR-AMT(WK-I)
                                 = WK-BRDC-ATHOR-AMT / 1000

      *                    이사회승인원화환산금액
                           COMPUTE XDJL4136-O-BRDC-ATHOR-WONC-AUC(WK-I)
